823
00:34:39,210 --> 00:34:41,530
Dinala mo ang mail
huli na kahapon.

824
00:34:41,530 --> 00:34:43,090
Ngunit malapit nang dumating ang mailman,

825
00:34:43,090 --> 00:34:44,380
